{"tid":2108940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紐約時報》宣佈將數碼新聞中心撤出香港搬到首爾 「國安法令新聞機構不安」","createTime":"2020-07-15T01:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T10:34:04.000Z","uid":7542,"like":548,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"2d76bf96dc509f28142cf7015db8e2acf0492766","tid":2108940,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:53:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">之前阿邊個邊個，又話國安法係定海神針嘅</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》指，過去數十年來，香港一直吸引不少英語新聞機構到當地設立亞洲總部，原因是對外國公司保持開放性、毗鄰中國大陸、而且沒有任何特別的審查限制。然而在「港版國安法」通過後已不再一樣，「中國通過影響廣泛的國安法，令新聞機構不安，並對香港作為亞洲新聞中心的前景產生不確定性」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200715/KL5MPL5V6AEIDGGD2SXNPMDX2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200715%2FKL5MPL5V6AEIDGGD2SXNPMDX2A%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=328fe732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200715%2FKL5MPL5V6AEIDGGD2SXNPMDX2A%2F&h=4b6b319e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200715/KL5MPL5V6AEIDGGD2SXNPMDX2A/</a>"},{"pid":"5644abafa8fcf3db4a174b6c8a1befe296b8f866","tid":2108940,"uid":6030,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"我屋企廁所都有支"},{"pid":"672d308183d751b85dfe805bfe01aa8eda865d2c","tid":2108940,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07e69c88d170d0d443c9efc9e41c5a4df3987e0","tid":2108940,"uid":8308,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:54:22.000Z","msg":"基本法話一定要係香港。。"},{"pid":"286192cca49fe903a97dcc31dd0a4ad702a10438","tid